00:10.020 --> 00:11.960
Testing your niche ideas.

00:12.030 --> 00:12.420
OK.

00:12.450 --> 00:14.960
So you now have a list of niche market ideas.

00:15.000 --> 00:19.470
The next step is to test the ideas to see if they are likely to be profitable for you.

00:19.470 --> 00:24.720
There are two very important elements to this which are demand and commercial intent.

00:24.720 --> 00:26.280
Demand is very important.

00:26.400 --> 00:28.870
You do not want to go for a niche that is very small.

00:28.950 --> 00:32.820
If you are not getting a good number of targeted visitors to your website then you are not going to

00:32.820 --> 00:33.570
make much money.

00:33.660 --> 00:37.080
If anything at all you need targeted visitors.

00:37.080 --> 00:39.960
These are people that have an interest in your chosen niche.

00:39.990 --> 00:44.220
This is cost effective and will increase your chances of achieving conversions.

00:44.220 --> 00:47.430
Don't be tempted to purchase broad traffic for your niche.

00:47.430 --> 00:52.230
There are a lot of vendors selling traffic from specific countries but this will just be a waste of

00:52.230 --> 00:53.100
money.

00:53.100 --> 00:55.890
The other important aspect is commercial intent.

00:55.920 --> 01:00.520
If the niche is large but nobody spends money in it then you need to forget about it.

01:00.570 --> 01:03.050
It doesn't matter if you have a real passion for the niche.

01:03.120 --> 01:06.840
If there is no money to be made then you are just wasting your time.

01:06.870 --> 01:09.590
You need to take the emotion out of your decision here.

01:09.630 --> 01:13.840
It is possible that the best niche on your list is something that you don't know much about.

01:13.860 --> 01:18.510
You need to ask yourself if you could get interested and passionate about it especially if it was to

01:18.510 --> 01:19.970
make you a lot of money.

01:20.080 --> 01:25.450
Niche size it is fairly easy and quick to see whether your niche is large enough or not.

