This is certainly a niche market idea worth pursuing further.

02:49.500 --> 02:53.690
You can use the google keyword planner to check all of your niche ideas quickly.

02:53.790 --> 02:55.670
What is the best size of niche.

02:55.680 --> 03:01.410
Well there is no hard and fast rule but we would recommend that the C keyword has a minimum of ten thousand

