03:48.510 --> 03:49.970
COMMERCIAL INTENT.

03:50.190 --> 03:55.350
OK so you have run all of your niche ideas through the google keyword planner and eliminated those were

03:55.350 --> 03:57.450
the sizes the nation's too small.

03:57.480 --> 04:01.200
The next step is to check for commercial intent at this point.

04:01.200 --> 04:04.920
We want to make the distinction between physical and digital products.

04:04.920 --> 04:09.690
You can become an affiliate for Amazon and promote their physical products physical products tend to

04:09.690 --> 04:11.810
sell more easily than digital products.

04:12.030 --> 04:16.090
But the commissions you can earn as an affiliate are usually a lot lower.

04:16.320 --> 04:21.310
As a new Amazon affiliate you will earn just 4 percent commission on physical products.

04:21.330 --> 04:25.260
This can amount to a few cents or a few dollars depending on the price of the product.

04:25.290 --> 04:29.790
It is a good idea to target high ticket items at Amazon if you want to make good money.

04:29.790 --> 04:34.510
A good example of this is flat screen TV ads which sell for 1000 dollars and upwards.

04:34.620 --> 04:37.940
Digital products are guides videos and software.

04:38.010 --> 04:41.940
They are something that the customer can instantly download or have access to once they have made their

04:41.940 --> 04:45.750
purchase because it is usually more difficult to sell digital products.

04:45.750 --> 04:49.440
The commissions are higher ranging from 30 percent to 100 percent.

04:49.440 --> 04:54.750
Normally you can expect the 50 percent commission on digital products to make money online niche.

04:54.750 --> 05:00.150
There are some examples of low price products offering 100 percent commission usually digital products

05:00.150 --> 05:03.930
will be in a funnel which we will cover in more detail later.

05:03.930 --> 05:09.260
The best niche market ideas have both physical and digital product opportunities there are lots of products

05:09.260 --> 05:14.120
of both types available for you to make a commission on some niche ideas will only have physical products

05:14.120 --> 05:16.750
available and some only digital products.

05:16.760 --> 05:23.060
This is fine as long as people within the niche you're buying using Amazon you can use Amazon to see

05:23.060 --> 05:25.590
if there's commercial intent for your niche ideas.

05:25.700 --> 05:29.420
Just go to Amazon.com and then enter your seed keyword.

05:29.420 --> 05:32.410
So let's continue with our example of Paleo diet.

05:32.450 --> 05:37.330
There are not going to be a lot of physical products for the paleo diet as it is all about food choices.

05:37.370 --> 05:41.790
What we did find is a lot of books and some of them with a high number of reviews.

05:41.960 --> 05:46.160
The review can as important as people that actually buy the products leave them.

05:46.160 --> 05:50.990
It is generally accepted that a single review on Amazon means that at least 10 people purchase the product

05:51.500 --> 05:53.590
and as many as a thousand.

05:53.600 --> 05:55.790
Only a small number of people will leave a review.

05:55.790 --> 06:01.450
So if there are hundreds or even thousands of reviews then this is a good sign of commercial intent.

06:01.610 --> 06:06.260
So run the remaining he said yes through Amazon and look out for review numbers.

06:06.260 --> 06:10.640
Ideally you want at least 100 reviews for a product to suggest good commercial intent.

06:10.640 --> 06:15.800
There will be related products as well and you can check the review numbers for these two using click

06:15.800 --> 06:16.790
bank.

06:16.790 --> 06:20.270
As you know click bank is the number one marketplace for digital products.

06:20.420 --> 06:25.330
So go to click bank dot com and into your seed keyword in the affiliate marketplace section.

06:25.370 --> 06:29.420
The first thing to do is note the number of products available for Paleo diet.

06:29.420 --> 06:34.580
There were over 40 products available at the time of writing which is a good sign of commercial intent.

06:34.580 --> 06:38.470
You can refine your search by changing the results to show the highest gravity.

06:38.480 --> 06:43.430
This is a measure of the number of sales of a particular product by affiliates in the last week.

06:43.430 --> 06:48.440
The top paleo diet product and click bank has a gravity of over sixty five and there are others with

06:48.440 --> 06:50.320
the gravity of around 50.

06:50.330 --> 06:54.200
This is all good as it shows sales are happening in this niche.

