07:18.380 --> 07:21.130
This means that money is being spent on ads.

07:21.320 --> 07:27.350
Google ads are not cheap and you can easily pay one dollar and upwards a click for the best keyword

07:27.350 --> 07:28.290
terms.

07:28.460 --> 07:32.960
Advertisers would not be spending this money if there was no commercial intent in their niche.

